reviewText: Good quality video, however, I would have preferred all "Lone Ranger" instead of "The Cisco Kid".  My biggest disappointment is the lack of closing credits.  Why they edited out the cast and credits is a mystery.  It's a big enough deal to make me look for another collection!
only 1 disc is the lone ranger the other disc is the cisco kid not what I was expecting

They could have better editing but by and large they brought a smile to my face.  I would have preferred to get 4 discs of the Lone Ranger but the Cisco Kid was also part of my youth.
